    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Connects up a series of data entries onto a matching series in a target <ref refid="classElement" kindref="compound">Element</ref>. Inspects each entry, and uses the &apos;stride_&apos; field to determine which should be its target. <verbatim>* Suppose we have a stride of +1. Then
* Src:      1   2   3   4   n
* Dest: 2   3   4   5   n+1
*
* Suppose we have a stride of -2. Then
* Src:      1   2   3   4   n
* Dest: -   -   1   2   n-2
* </verbatim> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
